        <div class="sect2">
          <h3 id="windows">Windows</h3>
          <div class="ulist">
            <ul>
              <li>
              <p>Download the latest stable release 
                <a href="https://github.com/RigsOfRods/rigs-of-rods/releases">here</a> (recommended)
              </p>
              </li>
              <li>
              <p>Preview builds for upcoming versions may be found 
                <a href="http://forum.rigsofrods.org/forum-21.html">here</a>
              </p>
              </li>
              <li>
              <p>If you want to build from source see 
                <a href="https://github.com/RigsOfRods/rigs-of-rods/wiki/Compile-(Windows)">Compiling on Windows</a>
              </p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sect2">
          <h3 id="linux">Linux</h3>
          <div class="ulist">
