              <p>Packages for various distributions: 
                <a href="http://rigsofrods.org/old-forum/forums/121-Support-Linux-Mac/113517/page-0001.html">here</a>
              </p>
              </li>
              <li>
              <p>Build from source, see 
                <a href="https://github.com/RigsOfRods/rigs-of-rods/wiki/Compile-(Linux)">Compiling on Linux</a>
              </p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
